Ventral idiosoma (
Fig. 8
). Sternal, genital, endopodal, ventral and anal shields fused to form ornamented composite shield with 13 pairs of setae, three pairs of lyrifissures and one pair of pores. Anal shield fused, unpaired post-anal seta shorter than para-anal setae, cribrum small, anal pores indistinct.
